ygData.msgSnippet: As a female tank, I am looking forward to creating a character on our new server.  Only problem is, I can t find any of my old emails telling me which one you
ygData.messageBody:
As a female tank, I am looking forward to creating a character on our new
server. Only problem is, I can't find any of my old emails telling me which
one you ladies decided on (I had to reformat my hard drive due to virus
infestation, caught immediately, so no harm done to anyone but me), and the
name of the guild that was created especially for us, by us. Someone please
fill me in? <blushes>
Sara, Povar
Valdaya, Rallos Zek
Ishtarre, Quellios, who will do her best to be in attendance at your
nuptials

Judy Tyrer wrote:

> From: Judy Tyrer <judy3t@...>
>
> Master Tarker Blazetoss invites you to attend the wedding of his
> apprentice Dnaice with Corellon. The wedding will take place on the
> Quellious server Sunday, Aug.7 at 5 PM Pacifc, 8 PM Eastern Daylight
> time at the Temple of Marr in North Freeport.
>
> ****
>
> I am Dnaice, a high elf wizard on Quellious server and, occasionally,
> Trisango a human cleric on Brell Serilis. My love, Corellon and I met
> in Norrath and know absolutely nothing about one another on any
> dimension outside of Norrath which, we feel, makes this romance and
> wedding extremely special. Our tale, which I must complete today, is
> posted on http://longroad.mpog.com under Tales/ Dnaice's Tale.
>
> Tigeress and Swiftlion, who were wed last weekend will be in
> attendance. I was priveleged to see their wedding and it was most
> spectacular. If you have never attended one, you must come. It is a
> grand and glorious spectacle.
>
> I look forward to getting to know other women who play, particularly
> roleplay. I would dearly love to create an all female hunting party. I
> just meet very few female tanks *smile*.
>
> Dnaice on Quellious Server
> Trisango on Brill Serilis
> Judy 3T on Terra
